race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: CYCLONE SEBAS (1) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 300m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. STARLIGHT DUKE (5) comes here off a placing in slick time (17.47) over 300m at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. SCOTCH AND WATER (2) placed two back in a Grade 4/5 at this track then not far away from a tricky draw last time when fifth (17.90) at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. BIG COOL KAOS (6) is right in the mix.
